  <brief_title>CARILLON Mitral Contour System® for Reducing Functional Mitral Regurgitation</brief_title>
  <acronym>REDUCE FMR</acronym>
  <official_title>The REDUCE FMR Trial: Safety and Efficacy of the CARILLON Mitral Contour System® in Reducing Functional Mitral Regurgitation (FMR) Associated With Heart Failure</official_title>
