  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this prospective, multi-center, randomized, double-blind trial is to assess
      the safety and efficacy of the CARILLON Mitral Contour System in treating functional mitral
      regurgitation (FMR) associated with heart failure, compared to a randomized Control group
      which is medically managed according to heart failure guidelines.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
